data.description: Home with Shop on 2.47+/- acres .  You will feel right at home as you step through the front door of this beautiful home. Enjoy time at home with 2 living areas, formal dining with fireplace, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car attached garage.  From the kitchen step outside to a covered patio and 2.47+/- acres to run and play. Shop with electricity, car lift, and a bathroom, 2 garage doors and 1 man door.  Plus additional 4 car carport next to house.  Loads of covered parking and room to roam. New septic and sprinkler system in 2020  Call today don't delay!
